# For EC2 Deployment:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Generate a new SECRET_KEY: python -c 'from django.core.management.utils import get_random_secret_key; print(get_random_secret_key())'
# 3. Set DEBUG=False
# 4. Add your EC2 public IP to ALLOWED_HOSTS
# 5. Change DB_PASSWORD to a strong password
